t5653.text: I’d like to thank all the black victims of assault, domestic violence, sexual trafficking, racism for coming out and speaking their story despite their being such a prejudice in society to this day.

t5654.text: I’d like to thank all the black people in my life for being so lovely to me and truely showing that the racist stereotypes white people depict black people as are completely false. I am so grateful you accept me into your lives so willingly.
